headline: TROW Q4 Deep Dive: Market Outflows, Fee Pressures, and Strategic Shifts Shape Results
summary: Investment management firm T. Rowe Price (NASDAQ:TROW) met Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q4 CY2025, with sales up 5.4% year on year to $1.94 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.44 per share was 1% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
